data.value: Larry is the founder of and pizza maker behind Lorenzo’s Pizzeria, which he launched in Oberlin in 1982. Inspired by his Uncle Augie, a renowned pizza maker in Cleveland, Larry has raised the bar so high on authentic Italian pizza that it’s hard to beat.

data.name: label2.Text
data.value: What restaurant can boast that it has a Registered Dietitian (R.D.) on staff? Lorenzo's. Mickey Cariglio is co-owner of Lorenzo’s and Larry’s wife. With a B.S. degree in dietetics from the University of Akron, Mickey literally “stirs the pot” with healthy ingredients in Lorenzo’s kitchen. Always on top of the latest dietary and health trends, Mickey makes sure that Lorenzo’s menu offers people of all ages healthful alternatives.
